{"id": "1429746109483319377", "channel_id": "1429746109483319377", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "卡斯托尔策划了第二次出逃，带着弟弟波吕克斯逃离提灯教会！\n\n📍 **完成下列关键任务，并为卡斯托尔找出逃生路线：**\n1、进入寝殿，喂波吕克斯吃下昏睡药丸\n2、带波吕克斯前往“地下货仓”，并将他藏入货箱待天亮后运出\n3、成功抵达“山洞”逃出提灯教会\n4、注意：\n✦ 抵达货仓前 可能会遇到灯卫盘问，利用圣子身份威慑他们以便继续前进；\n✦ 离开货仓后 灯卫将阻拦卡斯托尔前进，请尽量避开！若提前拾得武器，可杀死他们继续前进。\n\n🎁 守密人能找到几种逃跑路线？\n在评论区分享逃生图，找齐所有路线后将在明天解锁全服奖励：**内含无垢之芯×20、特批药剂×10 **\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nCastor plotted the second escape, fleeing the Church of the Lightbearers with his brother Pollux!\n\n📍 **Complete the following tasks and find an escape route for Castor:**\n1. Enter the bedchamber and feed Pollux the sleeping pill.\n2. Take the sedated Pollux to the \"Cellar\", hide him in a cargo box to be shipped out at dawn.\n3. Successfully reach the \"Cave Entrance\" to escape the Church of the Lightbearers.\n4. Notes:\n✦ If the Light Guards question Castor before he reaches the \"Cellar\", intimidate them with the very name of the Divus to proceed.\n✦ Light Guards will be hostile after Castor leaves the \"Cellar\", so avoid them if possible! Weapons collected beforehand can be used to kill them and proceed.\n\n🎁How many escape routes can you find? \nShare your escape maps in the comments! Once all routes are found, a server-wide reward will be unlocked tomorrow: **Pure Core×20, Special Potion Supply×10.**", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T08:20:35.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "dizzy2", "emoji_id": "1356083001926221874", "count": 13}, {"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "H_Discontent", "emoji_id": "1400771611971293214", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1429746110305669214", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3526738, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1429746